---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About | Venera Capital"
	description="Venera Capital is a private equity firm built on deep Central Asian expertise and global investment discipline."
>

	<!-- ── Page Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
	<section class="page-hero bg-navy">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="section-eyebrow">About the Firm</span>
			<h1 style="color:var(--white); font-weight:300; margin-bottom:0;">Who We Are</h1>
			<hr class="divider" />
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- ── Overview ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
	<section class="section bg-white">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="overview-grid">
				<div class="overview-main">
					<span class="section-eyebrow">Overview</span>
					<h2>A Private Equity Firm Built for Central Asia</h2>
					<hr class="divider" />
					<p class="lead">
						Venera Capital is a private equity firm dedicated to identifying, investing in, and building exceptional businesses across Central Asia. We combine global investment discipline with deep regional expertise.
					</p>
					<p style="color:var(--text-mid);">
						Founded with a clear vision to channel capital into Central Asia's most promising sectors, our firm brings together professionals with extensive backgrounds in international finance, operations, and the unique dynamics of the Kazakh, Uzbek, and broader Central Asian markets.
					</p>
					<p style="color:var(--text-mid);">
						We believe Central Asia represents one of the world's most compelling investment opportunities — a region rich in natural resources, a young and growing population, rapid urbanisation, and governments committed to economic modernisation. Venera Capital is uniquely positioned to help investors access these opportunities.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="overview-sidebar">
					<div class="sidebar-item">
						<h5>Investment Region</h5>
						<p>Kazakhstan, Uzbekistan, Kyrgyzstan, Tajikistan, and the broader Central Asian corridor</p>
					</div>
					<div class="sidebar-item">
						<h5>Strategy</h5>
						<p>Control and co-control investments in growth-stage and established businesses across key sectors</p>
					</div>
					<div class="sidebar-item">
						<h5>Horizon</h5>
						<p>Long-term investment perspective with a focus on sustainable value creation</p>
					</div>
					<div class="sidebar-item">
						<h5>Sectors</h5>
						<p>Energy, Technology, Real Estate, Infrastructure, Financial Services, Consumer</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- ── Philosophy ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
	<section class="section bg-off-white">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header-centered">
				<span class="section-eyebrow">Investment Philosophy</span>
				<h2>Our Guiding Principles</h2>
				<hr class="divider divider-center" />
			</div>
			<div class="principles-grid">
				<div class="principle-card">
					<div class="p-header">
						<span class="p-num">01</span>
						<h3>Long-Term Value Creation</h3>
					</div>
					<p>We invest with a multi-year horizon, refusing to sacrifice sustainable growth for short-term financial engineering. Our portfolio companies benefit from a patient capital partner that measures success in the strength of businesses built, not just returns generated.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="principle-card">
					<div class="p-header">
						<span class="p-num">02</span>
						<h3>Operational Partnership</h3>
					</div>
					<p>We are active investors. Our team works alongside management to identify strategic opportunities, strengthen operations, and build the organisational capabilities required for sustained competitive advantage. We bring both capital and expertise to every investment.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="principle-card">
					<div class="p-header">
						<span class="p-num">03</span>
						<h3>Regional Expertise</h3>
					</div>
					<p>Central Asia has its own unique dynamics — regulatory frameworks, business cultures, and market structures that differ meaningfully from other emerging markets. Our deep regional knowledge and established relationships allow us to navigate these complexities and turn them into advantages.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="principle-card">
					<div class="p-header">
						<span class="p-num">04</span>
						<h3>Responsible Investing</h3>
					</div>
					<p>We are committed to building businesses that create value not just for our investors, but for the communities and economies in which they operate. Environmental, social, and governance considerations are integrated into our investment process and portfolio management.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- ── Why Central Asia ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
	<section class="section bg-navy">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="region-grid">
				<div class="region-text">
					<span class="section-eyebrow">The Opportunity</span>
					<h2 style="color:var(--white); font-weight:300;">Why Central Asia</h2>
					<hr class="divider" />
					<p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);">
						Central Asia is at an inflection point. The five nations of the region — Kazakhstan, Uzbekistan, Kyrgyzstan, Tajikistan, and Turkmenistan — are home to over 75 million people and sit at the crossroads of major global trade routes.
					</p>
					<p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);">
						Significant natural resources, a young and increasingly educated workforce, rapid digitisation, and determined economic reform agendas are creating a compelling environment for patient, sophisticated capital.
					</p>
					<a href="/focus" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:1.25rem;">Explore Our Investment Focus</a>
				</div>
				<div class="region-factors">
					<div class="factor">
						<div class="f-arrow">→</div>
						<div>
							<h5 style="color:var(--white);">Strategic Location</h5>
							<p>At the heart of the historic Silk Road, connecting China, Russia, Europe, and South Asia</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="factor">
						<div class="f-arrow">→</div>
						<div>
							<h5 style="color:var(--white);">Resource Rich</h5>
							<p>Abundant oil, gas, minerals, and agricultural land driving sustained economic development</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="factor">
						<div class="f-arrow">→</div>
						<div>
							<h5 style="color:var(--white);">Growing Middle Class</h5>
							<p>Rapidly expanding consumer base with rising disposable incomes and aspirations</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="factor">
						<div class="f-arrow">→</div>
						<div>
							<h5 style="color:var(--white);">Reform-Oriented Governments</h5>
							<p>Governments actively liberalising economies and welcoming private and foreign investment</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- ── Contact CTA ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
	<section class="section-sm bg-white">
		<div class="container" style="text-align:center; max-width:600px;">
			<span class="section-eyebrow">Work With Us</span>
			<h2>Ready to Connect?</h2>
			<hr class="divider divider-center" />
			<p style="color:var(--text-mid); margin-bottom:2rem;">
				We welcome enquiries from investors, management teams, and businesses across the region.
			</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Venera Capital</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>

<style>
	.lead {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: var(--text-dark);
	}

	.overview-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
		gap: 5rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.overview-sidebar {
		border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
		padding-left: 3rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2.25rem;
	}

	.sidebar-item h5  { color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
	.sidebar-item p   { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; }

	.principles-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 1.5px;
		background: var(--border);
		border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
	}

	.principle-card {
		background: var(--white);
		padding: 2.75rem 2.25rem;
		transition: background var(--transition);
	}

	.principle-card:hover { background: var(--off-white); }

	.p-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: baseline;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.p-num {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: var(--gold);
		opacity: 0.35;
		line-height: 1;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.principle-card h3 { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 500; margin: 0; }
	.principle-card p  { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.72; margin: 0; }

	.region-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 5rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.region-factors {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.factor { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; align-items: flex-start; }

	.f-arrow {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--gold);
		flex-shrink: 0;
		margin-top: 0.05rem;
	}

	.factor p {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: rgba(255,255,255,0.52);
		margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.overview-grid,
		.region-grid    { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
		.principles-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.overview-sidebar {
			border-left: none;
			padding-left: 0;
			border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
			padding-top: 2.5rem;
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.overview-sidebar { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
	}
</style>
